  m_text: "Alexandra\n\nD\xFC\u015F\xFCk can ve sald\u0131r\u0131 g\xFCc\xFCne sahip
    olmas\u0131na ra\u011Fmen, Alexandra \xFCst\xFCn stratejik zek\xE2s\u0131yla
    sava\u015F\u0131n gidi\u015Fat\u0131n\u0131 de\u011Fi\u015Ftirebilir. G\xFCc\xFCn\xFC
    pusulalar\u0131ndan alan bu kart, do\u011Fru kullan\u0131ld\u0131\u011F\u0131nda
    rakibin planlar\u0131n\u0131 bozabilecek \xF6nemli f\u0131rsatlar yarat\u0131r.\n\nEtkile\u015Fimde
    Bulundu\u011Fu Kartlar\n\u2022 Amiralin Pusulas\u0131\n\u2022 Pusula\n\u2022
    Bozuk Pusula\n\nKart T\xFCr\xFC\nArka S\u0131ra Kart\u0131"
