      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "**Charles Darwin**\r\n\r\nKeskin zek\xE2s\u0131 ve y\u0131llar s\xFCren
    ara\u015Ft\u0131rmalar\u0131 sayesinde Charles Darwin, canl\u0131lar\u0131n g\xFC\xE7l\xFC
    ve zay\u0131f y\xF6nlerini herkesten daha iyi bilir. Evrim \xFCzerine yapt\u0131\u011F\u0131
    \xE7al\u0131\u015Fmalar, rakiplerinin a\xE7\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131 h\u0131zla
    tespit etmesine ve \xF6l\xFCmc\xFCl hassasiyetle sald\u0131rmas\u0131na olanak
    tan\u0131r.\r\n\r\nY\xFCksek sald\u0131r\u0131 g\xFCc\xFCne sahip olmas\u0131na
    ra\u011Fmen fiziksel olarak olduk\xE7a k\u0131r\u0131lgand\u0131r. Kendini savunmaktan
    \xE7ok g\xF6zlem yapmaya ve rakibinin zay\u0131f noktalar\u0131n\u0131 ortaya
    \xE7\u0131karmaya odaklanan Darwin, korundu\u011Fu s\xFCrece sava\u015F alan\u0131nda
    b\xFCy\xFCk bir tehdit olu\u015Fturabilir.\r\n\r\n**Etkile\u015Fimde Bulundu\u011Fu
    Kartlar**\r\n\u2022 Yok\r\n\r\n**Kart T\xFCr\xFC**\r\nArka S\u0131ra Kart\u0131\r\n"
