      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "**Kumandan**\r\n\r\nD\xFC\u015F\xFCk dayan\u0131kl\u0131l\u0131\u011F\u0131na
    ra\u011Fmen keskin zek\xE2s\u0131 ve sava\u015F alan\u0131n\u0131 okuma yetene\u011Fi
    sayesinde rakiplerinden bir ad\u0131m \xF6nde hareket eder. Do\u011Frudan g\xFC\xE7
    kullanmak yerine stratejileri ve \xF6zel pusulalar\u0131yla sava\u015F\u0131n
    ak\u0131\u015F\u0131n\u0131 kontrol eder.\r\n\r\nDo\u011Fru hamlelerle k\xFC\xE7\xFCk
    bir avantaj\u0131 b\xFCy\xFCk bir zafere d\xF6n\xFC\u015Ft\xFCrebilen Kumandan,
    korunmas\u0131 gereken \xF6nemli bir stratejik birimdir.\r\n\r\n**Etkile\u015Fimde
    Bulundu\u011Fu Kartlar**\r\n\u2022 Kumandan Pusulas\u0131\r\n\u2022 Hileli Pusula\r\n\r\n**Kart
    T\xFCr\xFC**\r\nArka S\u0131ra Kart\u0131\r\n"
