  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "**Gece Bek\xE7isi**\r\n\r\nGecenin karanl\u0131\u011F\u0131nda g\xF6rev
    yapan Gece Bek\xE7isi, d\xFC\u015Fman hareketlerini izleyerek tehlikeleri daha
    ortaya \xE7\u0131kmadan fark eder. Rakibin sald\u0131r\u0131 zaman\u0131n\u0131
    ve y\xF6n\xFCn\xFC sezebildi\u011Fi i\xE7in g\xFC\xE7l\xFC bir savunma hatt\u0131
    olu\u015Fturur.\r\n\r\nAncak g\xF6zlem yetene\u011Fini sald\u0131r\u0131ya d\xF6n\xFC\u015Ft\xFCrmekte
    zorlan\u0131r. Y\xFCksek dayan\u0131kl\u0131l\u0131\u011F\u0131 sayesinde sava\u015F
    alan\u0131nda uzun s\xFCre kalabilir, fakat s\u0131n\u0131rl\u0131 sald\u0131r\u0131
    g\xFCc\xFCyle daha \xE7ok tak\u0131m\u0131n\u0131 korumaya odaklan\u0131r.\r\n\r\n**Etkile\u015Fimde
    Bulundu\u011Fu Kartlar**\r\n\u2022 Yok\r\n\r\n**Kart T\xFCr\xFC**\r\n\xD6n S\u0131ra
    Kart\u0131\r\n"
