    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "**Hintli**\r\n\r\nSava\u015F alan\u0131nda \xF6zel bir g\xFCce sahip olmamas\u0131na
    ra\u011Fmen, Hintli dengeli yap\u0131s\u0131 ve kararl\u0131l\u0131\u011F\u0131yla
    her duruma uyum sa\u011Flayabilen bir sava\u015F\xE7\u0131d\u0131r. Ne en g\xFC\xE7l\xFC
    ne de en zay\u0131f olan bu kart, do\u011Fru zamanda kullan\u0131ld\u0131\u011F\u0131nda
    tak\u0131m\u0131n\u0131n ihtiya\xE7 duydu\u011Fu deste\u011Fi sa\u011Flayabilir.\r\n\r\nBasit
    g\xF6r\xFCnse de istikrar\u0131 onun en b\xFCy\xFCk avantaj\u0131d\u0131r. Hem
    \xF6n safta m\xFCcadele edebilir hem de arka saflarda tak\u0131m\u0131na katk\u0131
    sa\u011Flayabilir.\r\n\r\n**Etkile\u015Fimde Bulundu\u011Fu Kartlar**\r\n\u2022
    Yok\r\n\r\n**Kart T\xFCr\xFC**\r\n\xD6n ve Arka S\u0131ra Kart\u0131\r\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
